OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,FHero PCSO Barry Calder tells about the
OL,7,Fsupport he has received while
OL,8,Fcompleting five marathons in just five
OL,9,Fdays
OL,11,FA Police Community Support Officer
OL,12,Fwhose decisive action saved the life
OL,13,Fof a child who was stabbed eight times
OL,14,Fduring the Southport attack has
OL,15,Fcompleted five marathons in five days.
OL,17,FBarry Calder was one of the first
OL,18,Fresponders to arrive at the scene and
OL,19,Fimmediately began triaging injured
OL,20,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783703991
OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,F"I looked across the street and just
OL,7,Fsaw a pair of very tiny, small legs
OL,8,Fand initially thought they were
OL,9,Funderneath a transit van, and then I
OL,10,Fremember rolling her over and finding
OL,11,Fsix more stab wounds in her back," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FBarry previously served for more than
OL,15,F30 years with the Metropolitan Police.
OL,16,FHis roles included Armed Response
OL,17,FOfficer and Police Medic, and he dealt
OL,18,Fwith major incidents such as the
OL,19,FWestminster Bridge terrorist attack
OL,20,Fbefore retiring in 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783703991
OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,FBut he missed the job so much that in
OL,7,F2024, he joined Merseyside Police as a
OL,8,FPCSO.
OL,10,FHe was only six weeks into training
OL,11,Fwhen Axel Rudakubana launched his
OL,12,Fattack, and said the scene that met
OL,13,Fhim that day was truly horrific.
OL,15,F"I probably wouldn't be able to put
OL,16,Finto words how shocking and horrific
OL,17,Fit was. People shouldn't ever have to
OL,18,Fsee a child injured, never mind
OL,19,Fmultiple children injured," Barry said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
