CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783703991
OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,FThe children had been attending a
OL,7,FTaylor Swift-themed dance and yoga
OL,8,Fworkshop in 2024.
OL,10,FElsie Dot Stancombe, 7, Alice Aguiar,
OL,11,F9, and Bebe King, 6, died in the
OL,12,Fattack. Eight other children and two
OL,13,Fadults were physically injured.
OL,15,FThey included "Natasha" who was
OL,16,Fstabbed while trying to shield her
OL,17,Flittle sister from the attacker.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
