OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783703991
OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,FA court order is in place protecting
OL,7,Fthe identity of all the injured girls.
OL,8,FNatasha is not this child's real name.
OL,9,FWe have called her mum Louise and
OL,10,Fchanged her voice.
OL,12,FLouise told ITV News: "He packed her
OL,13,Fwounds and I genuinely hand on heart
OL,14,Fbelieve if he hadn't done that in that
OL,15,Fmoment we would be sat here in a
OL,16,Fcompletely different situation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783703991
OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,FShe praised the immense bravery shown
OL,7,Fby both her daughters and believes
OL,8,Fthat by placing herself in harm's way,
OL,9,Fher eldest daughter saved her sister's
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,F"As much as I hate talking about what
OL,13,Fhappened that day, I think it speaks
OL,14,Fvolumes for the bravery and the love
OL,15,Fthat she has for her family without
OL,16,Fher. Without her, I don't think her
OL,17,Flittle sister would be here either,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783703991
OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,FBoth sisters were treated for stab
OL,7,Fwounds at Alder Hey Children's
OL,8,Fhospital in Liverpool.
OL,10,FBarry said Natasha's injuries were so
OL,11,Fsevere that he feared she wouldn't
OL,12,Fsurvive. But they've since met and now
OL,13,Fshare a bond which he said will never
OL,14,Fbe broken.
OL,16,FShe was at his side as he set off on a
OL,17,Fhuge charity challenge of five
OL,18,Fmarathons in five days, covering 131
OL,19,Fmiles and visiting every operational
OL,20,Fpolice station in Merseyside.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1783703991
OL,3,CSouthport PCSO does 5 marathons after
OL,4,Csaving girl's life
OL,6,FBarry described it as a deeply
OL,7,Fpersonal mission, raising money for
OL,8,Flocal causes and mental health support
OL,9,Ffor those living with trauma.
OL,11,FHe sought help from Police Care UK in
OL,12,Fthe aftermath of the attack ` a
OL,13,Fcharity that provides free and
OL,14,Fconfidential support for serving and
OL,15,Fveteran police officers and staff,
OL,16,Fvolunteers, and their families.
OL,18,F"I insisted to everyone that I was OK,
OL,19,Fand I clearly wasn't, and things
OL,20,Fslowly got worse," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
